Quote: <i>Cyclosorus penniger (Forst.f.) Copel.</i> Common name: <i>Gully fern</i> Maori name: <i>Piupiu </i>... This common fern is found in woods throughout New Zealand. It has been placed in <i>Polypodium, Goniopteris, Aspidium, Nephrodium, Dryopteris</i>, and <i>Thelypteris.</i> [Williams identifies as <i>Blechnum</i> spp.]
